<?php $__env->startSection('postContent'); ?><p><strong>Purpose:</strong></p>
<p>To develop an understanding of a design process and practical skills through the manufacture of a small guitar. This will enable students to develop confidence in both applying a design process and fabricating a complex solution.</p>
<p><strong>Content:</strong></p>
<p>All students will make a small guitar with the option to design certain elements in order to personalize their instrument. They will develop manufacturing skills through working with a range of hard materials. Students will be taught practical skills and the expectations of safe workshop practice.</p>
<p><strong>Assessment:</strong></p>
<p>Portfolio work and practical solution.</p><?php $__env->stopSection(); ?>
